query:
SELECT ef.id, ef.eventoId, ef.formandoId, ef.status, ef.dataExecucao, f.nome 
FROM execucaoFormando ef 
JOIN formandos f ON ef.formandoId = f.id 
WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Jean-Karlo%' 
LIMIT 5
